      <title>塞西称埃及不能参与驱逐巴勒斯坦人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/egypt-can-t-play-role-in-displacing-palestinians-el-sisi-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普建议将加沙地带的居民迁移至埃及和约旦，埃及总统阿卜杜勒·法塔赫·塞西表示，埃及不能参与强制巴勒斯坦人迁出加沙的行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/egypt-can-t-play-role-in-displacing-palestinians-el-sisi-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 15:01:10 GMT</pubDate>
