    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨在竞选中抨击对手民粹主义</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/scholz-accuses-rival-of-populism-in-election-campaign-broadside</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨对下个月提前大选的保守党领跑者进行了严厉的人身攻击，指责弗里德里希·梅尔茨诉诸民粹主义，并在移民问题上采取强硬立场，与极右翼势力勾结。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/scholz-accuses-rival-of-populism-in-election-campaign-broadside</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 14:13:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
